---
export const prerender = true;
---
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Il Corriere Digitale — Blog Editoriale Premium</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merriweather:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Noise overlay -->
  <div class="noise"></div>

  <!-- Back button -->
  <a href="/dev/portfolio" class="back-btn">
    <span class="back-arrow">&larr;</span> Torna al Portfolio
  </a>

  <!-- Breaking news ticker -->
  <div class="ticker">
    <div class="ticker-label">ULTIME NOTIZIE</div>
    <div class="ticker-track">
      <div class="ticker-content">
        <span>Nuovo studio rivela: il 78% dei lettori preferisce contenuti long-form</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Tecnologia e sostenibilità: le tendenze del 2026</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Intervista esclusiva con il fondatore della startup italiana più innovativa</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Il futuro dell'editoria digitale: report completo disponibile</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Nuovo studio rivela: il 78% dei lettori preferisce contenuti long-form</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Tecnologia e sostenibilità: le tendenze del 2026</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Intervista esclusiva con il fondatore della startup italiana più innovativa</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Il futuro dell'editoria digitale: report completo disponibile</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <header class="hero fade-in">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <div class="hero-category">Articolo in evidenza</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">L'arte di raccontare storie nell'era digitale</h1>
        <p class="hero-excerpt">
          Un'esplorazione profonda di come la narrativa sta evolvendo,
          tra intelligenza artificiale, giornalismo immersivo e nuove forme
          di coinvolgimento del lettore.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-meta">
          <span class="hero-author">di <strong>Marco Rossi</strong></span>
          <span class="hero-date">21 Marzo 2026</span>
          <span class="hero-read">12 min lettura</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1499750310107-5fef28a66643?w=1200&h=500&fit=crop&auto=format&q=80" alt="Foto di copertina" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Categories -->
  <nav class="categories fade-in">
    <div class="categories-inner">
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill active">Tutti</a>
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill">Tecnologia</a>
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill">Cultura</a>
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill">Economia</a>
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill">Scienza</a>
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill">Opinioni</a>
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill">Longform</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Main content -->
  <main class="content">
    <div class="content-inner">
      <!-- Articles grid -->
      <div class="articles">
        <article class="card card-featured fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486312338219-ce68d2c6f44d?w=400&h=250&fit=crop&auto=format&q=80" alt="Immagine articolo" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
            <div class="card-category-badge">Tecnologia</div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title">Come l'intelligenza artificiale sta ridefinendo il giornalismo investigativo</h2>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Dalle redazioni di tutto il mondo emergono nuovi strumenti che amplificano le capacità dei reporter, senza sostituire il tocco umano.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Giulia Bianchi</span>
              <span class="card-time">8 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504711434969-e33886168d4c?w=400&h=250&fit=crop&auto=format&q=80" alt="Img" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-category-tag">Cultura</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Rinascimento digitale: i musei italiani conquistano il metaverso</h3>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Visite virtuali, NFT d'arte e esperienze immersive stanno trasformando il modo in cui fruiamo il patrimonio culturale.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Luca Verdi</span>
              <span class="card-time">6 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1488190211105-8b0e65b80b4e?w=400&h=250&fit=crop&auto=format&q=80" alt="Img" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-category-tag">Economia</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Startup italiane: il boom silenzioso che nessuno racconta</h3>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Oltre 200 startup hanno raccolto finanziamenti record nel primo trimestre. Un ecosistema in fermento.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Anna Ferretti</span>
              <span class="card-time">5 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1456324504439-367cee3b3c32?w=400&h=250&fit=crop&auto=format&q=80" alt="Img" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-category-tag">Scienza</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">La corsa allo spazio privato: l'Italia gioca la sua partita</h3>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Da Avio a nuove realtà emergenti, il settore spaziale italiano si prepara a una nuova era.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Paolo Neri</span>
              <span class="card-time">7 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519389950473-47ba0277781c?w=400&h=250&fit=crop&auto=format&q=80" alt="Img" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-category-tag">Opinioni</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Perché abbiamo bisogno di un nuovo patto con la tecnologia</h3>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Non si tratta di rifiutare il progresso. Si tratta di scegliere quale progresso vogliamo.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Elena Marchi</span>
              <span class="card-time">4 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Pull Quote -->
        <blockquote class="pull-quote fade-in">
          <div class="pull-quote-mark">&ldquo;</div>
          <p>Il giornalismo non morirà mai. Cambierà forma, cambierà strumenti, ma la necessità umana di raccontare e ascoltare storie resterà eterna.</p>
          <cite>— Maria Grazia Colombo, direttrice editoriale</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=400&h=250&fit=crop&auto=format&q=80" alt="Img" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-category-tag">Longform</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Sei mesi nell'Artico: diario di una spedizione climatica</h3>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Un reportage immersivo dalla prima linea del cambiamento climatico, tra ghiacci che si sciolgono e comunità che resistono.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Davide Costa</span>
              <span class="card-time">18 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486312338219-ce68d2c6f44d?w=400&h=250&fit=crop&auto=format&q=80" alt="Img" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-category-tag">Tecnologia</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Il codice sorgente della democrazia: open source e trasparenza</h3>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Come il software libero sta influenzando la governance e la partecipazione civica in tutta Europa.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Roberto Sala</span>
              <span class="card-time">9 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-sticky">
          <div class="sidebar-section glass-card fade-in">
            <h4 class="sidebar-title">Più Letti</h4>
            <ol class="most-read">
              <li>
                <span class="most-read-num">01</span>
                <a href="#">L'algoritmo che prevede le crisi economiche con 6 mesi di anticipo</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="most-read-num">02</span>
                <a href="#">Vivere senza smartphone: l'esperimento che ha cambiato la mia vita</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="most-read-num">03</span>
                <a href="#">Roma 2030: il piano urbanistico che divide gli esperti</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="most-read-num">04</span>
                <a href="#">Perché i giovani italiani tornano dai borghi</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="most-read-num">05</span>
                <a href="#">L'ultimo treno per la transizione energetica</a>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-section glass-card fade-in">
            <h4 class="sidebar-title">Newsletter</h4>
            <p class="sidebar-text">Ricevi ogni mattina le storie che contano. Niente spam, solo giornalismo di qualità.</p>
            <form class="newsletter-form">
              <input type="email" placeholder="La tua email" class="newsletter-input" />
              <button type="button" class="newsletter-btn">Iscriviti</button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-section glass-card fade-in">
            <h4 class="sidebar-title">Tag Popolari</h4>
            <div class="tag-cloud">
              <a href="#" class="tag">Intelligenza Artificiale</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Clima</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Startup</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Europa</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Design</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Innovazione</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Sostenibilità</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Cultura</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Floating decorations -->
  <div class="floating-circle c1"></div>
  <div class="floating-circle c2"></div>
  <div class="floating-circle c3"></div>

  <footer class="footer fade-in">
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <h3>Il Corriere Digitale</h3>
        <p>Giornalismo indipendente per menti curiose.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="#">Chi siamo</a>
        <a href="#">Redazione</a>
        <a href="#">Pubblicità</a>
        <a href="#">Contatti</a>
        <a href="#">Privacy</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 Il Corriere Digitale. Tutti i diritti riservati.</div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          const el = entry.target;
          const delay = el.dataset.delay || 0;
          setTimeout(() => el.classList.add('visible'), Number(delay));
          observer.unobserve(el);
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.1 });

    document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in').forEach((el, i) => {
      el.dataset.delay = (i % 5) * 100;
      observer.observe(el);
    });
  </script>

  <style>
    /* ===== RESET & BASE ===== */
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Source Sans 3', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* Custom scrollbar */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #f5f5f5; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #dc2626; border-radius: 4px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #b91c1c; }

    /* Noise overlay */
    .noise {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9999;
      opacity: 0.03;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      background-repeat: repeat;
      background-size: 256px 256px;
    }

    /* Fade-in animation */
    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    }
    .fade-in.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* Floating circles */
    .floating-circle {
      position: fixed;
      border-radius: 50%;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -1;
      opacity: 0.05;
      background: #dc2626;
    }
    .c1 { width: 400px; height: 400px; top: 10%; right: -100px; animation: floatA 20s ease-in-out infinite; }
    .c2 { width: 250px; height: 250px; bottom: 20%; left: -80px; animation: floatB 25s ease-in-out infinite; }
    .c3 { width: 150px; height: 150px; top: 60%; right: 10%; animation: floatA 18s ease-in-out infinite reverse; }
    @keyframes floatA {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
      33% { transform: translate(30px, -20px) scale(1.05); }
      66% { transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.95); }
    }
    @keyframes floatB {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
      50% { transform: translate(40px, -30px); }
    }

    /* ===== BACK BUTTON ===== */
    .back-btn {
      position: fixed;
      top: 58px;
      left: 20px;
      z-index: 1000;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(220,38,38,0.2);
      border-radius: 50px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .back-btn:hover {
      background: #dc2626;
      color: #fff;
      border-color: #dc2626;
      transform: translateX(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 25px rgba(220,38,38,0.25);
    }
    .back-arrow { font-size: 1.1rem; transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
    .back-btn:hover .back-arrow { transform: translateX(-3px); }

    /* ===== TICKER ===== */
    .ticker {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 999;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      height: 40px;
      background: #dc2626;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .ticker-label {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      padding: 0 20px;
      background: #1a1a1a;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    }
    .ticker-track { flex: 1; overflow: hidden; }
    .ticker-content {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 30px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      animation: ticker 40s linear infinite;
    }
    .ticker-dot {
      width: 5px; height: 5px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    @keyframes ticker {
      0% { transform: translateX(0); }
      100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }

    /* ===== HERO ===== */
    .hero { margin-top: 40px; padding: 80px 5vw 60px; }
    .hero-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-category {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: #dc2626;
      border: 1.5px solid #dc2626;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Merriweather', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #dc2626 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .hero-excerpt {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero-meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 20px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #888;
    }
    .hero-meta strong { color: #1a1a1a; }
    .hero-image {
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .hero-image img {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 4/3;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }
    .hero-image-lines {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      opacity: 0.15;
    }
    .hero-image-lines div {
      width: 60%; height: 3px;
      background: #aaa;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    /* ===== CATEGORIES ===== */
    .categories { padding: 0 5vw; margin-bottom: 50px; }
    .categories-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .cat-pill {
      padding: 8px 22px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #666;
      background: #f7f7f7;
      border: 1.5px solid transparent;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cat-pill:hover, .cat-pill.active {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626, #ef4444);
      color: #fff;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(220,38,38,0.3);
    }

    /* ===== MAIN CONTENT ===== */
    .content { padding: 0 5vw 80px; }
    .content-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
      gap: 50px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .articles {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    /* ===== CARDS ===== */
    .card {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
      transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(220,38,38,0.15);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    .card-featured {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #fef2f2 100%);
      border-color: rgba(220,38,38,0.1);
    }
    .card-featured .card-image img { aspect-ratio: 16/8; }
    .card-image { overflow: hidden; border-radius: 10px; }
    .card-image img {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      border-radius: 10px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    }
    .card:hover .card-image img { transform: scale(1.08); }
    .card-category-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: 12px;
      left: 12px;
      background: #dc2626;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    .card-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
    .card-category-tag {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: #dc2626;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .card-title {
      font-family: 'Merriweather', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: #111;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .card:hover .card-title { color: #dc2626; }
    .card-featured .card-title { font-size: 1.4rem; }
    .card-excerpt {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .card-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: #999;
    }
    .card-author { font-weight: 600; color: #555; }

    /* ===== PULL QUOTE ===== */
    .pull-quote {
      position: relative;
      padding: 50px 40px 40px 80px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2, #fff);
      border-radius: 0 16px 16px 0;
    }
    .pull-quote-mark {
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      left: 20px;
      font-family: 'Merriweather', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 5rem;
      color: #dc2626;
      opacity: 0.2;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .pull-quote p {
      font-family: 'Merriweather', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .pull-quote cite {
      font-style: normal;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #dc2626;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ===== SIDEBAR ===== */
    .sidebar-sticky {
      position: sticky;
      top: 60px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 30px;
    }
    .glass-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(220,38,38,0.08);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 28px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .glass-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(220,38,38,0.2);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(220,38,38,0.06);
    }
    .sidebar-title {
      font-family: 'Merriweather', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #dc2626;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .most-read {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .most-read li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .most-read-num {
      font-family: 'Merriweather', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #eee;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      line-height: 1;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .most-read li:hover .most-read-num { color: #dc2626; }
    .most-read a {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: #333;
      text-decoration: none;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .most-read a:hover { color: #dc2626; }
    .sidebar-text {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .newsletter-form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .newsletter-input {
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border: 1.5px solid #e5e5e5;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-family: inherit;
      transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
      outline: none;
    }
    .newsletter-input:focus { border-color: #dc2626; }
    .newsletter-btn {
      padding: 12px;
      background: #dc2626;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .newsletter-btn:hover {
      background: #b91c1c;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(220,38,38,0.3);
    }
    .tag-cloud { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
    .tag {
      padding: 6px 14px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #666;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      border-radius: 50px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .tag:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626, #ef4444);
      color: #fff;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
    .footer {
      background: #0a0a0a;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 60px 5vw;
    }
    .footer-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-brand h3 {
      font-family: 'Merriweather', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .footer-brand p {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .footer-links a {
      color: #888;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: #dc2626; }
    .footer-copy {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: #555;
      border-top: 1px solid #222;
      padding-top: 24px;
    }

    /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .content-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .sidebar-sticky { position: static; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 30px; }
      .hero { padding: 60px 5vw 40px; }
      .card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .card-image img { aspect-ratio: 16/9; }
      .back-btn { top: 48px; left: 12px; padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 0.78rem; }
      .pull-quote { padding: 40px 24px 30px 40px; }
      .pull-quote-mark { font-size: 3rem; left: 10px; }
      .pull-quote p { font-size: 1rem; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .hero-title { font-size: 1.6rem; }
      .hero-meta { flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
      .categories-inner { gap: 6px; }
      .cat-pill { padding: 6px 14px; font-size: 0.75rem; }
    }
  </style>
